videos.description: Kansas' Devon Dotson lobs an alley-oop to Ocahi Agbaji, who rises and flushes the dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Agbaji spikes oop for Kansas

videos.description: Kevin Samuel gets up for viscous put-back slam over Kansas' defenders.
videos.headline: Samuel throws down sick put-back slam

videos.description: Jayhawks' Devon Dotson gets beat off the dribble and hustles back to reject Alex Robinson's layup attempt.
videos.headline: Dotson elevates for monster block
